item.title: FAQ
item.description: Question Index:23 Seattle, WA I went for astrophysics. I’m currently looking for a full time position or paid projects. Outside of that I do game development full time and stream. In order of expertise / comfort: C, Unix/Bash Shell, Python, Java, C#, HTML/CSS, JS, PHP, MSSQL, MySQL, BASIC, Powershell. Void Linux (XFCE) Ryzen 7 1700, 16GB DDR4, Rx 590 8GB, 512GB M.2 NVMe SSD C(99), Cmake, and Unix Shell C forces me to look at each individual part of what I’m working on, as well as stick to a standard that is relatively portable.
